  <summary>11/1/2000--Introduced.
Electronic Marketplace Ownership Disclosure Act - Requires the Federal Trade Commission to prohibit unfair and deceptive acts and practices in the operation of an electronic marketplace by requiring electronic marketplace operators to disclose the equity ownership, control, and management of such marketplaces.</summary>
